<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>一般社団法人デザインシップ</title>
<meta name="description" content="一般社団法人デザインシップ。次世代の産業に貢献するデザイン人材の輩出。日本最大級のデザインカンファレンスを主催。">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  --black: #000000;
  --white: #ffffff;
  --gray: #888888;
  --dark-gray: #1a1a1a;
  --magenta: #E91E8C;
  --purple: #7B2FBE;
  --red: #FF1744;
  --yellow: #FFD600;
  --blue: #304FFE;
  --ease-out-expo: cubic-bezier(.19, 1, .22, 1);
  --duration: 1.3s;
}

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; background: var(--black); overflow-x: hidden; }

body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  background: var(--black);
  color: var(--white);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

::selection { background: var(--magenta); color: var(--white); }
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

/* ---- COMMON SECTION STYLES ---- */
.section-pad {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 140px 40px;
  text-align: center;
}

.section-label {
  font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px);
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--magenta);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1.3;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.section-desc {
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1.2vw, 16px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  line-height: 2;
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* ---- REVEAL ---- */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: opacity var(--duration) var(--ease-out-expo), transform var(--duration) var(--ease-out-expo);
}
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
.delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

/* ---- HERO ---- */
.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  width: 100vw;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}

canvas#fluid {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  z-index: 0;
}

.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  pointer-events: none;
  padding-bottom: 10vh;
}

.hero-logo-img {
  height: 140px;
  width: auto;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.6));
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 1s ease 0.3s;
  pointer-events: auto;
}
.hero.loaded .hero-logo-img { opacity: 1; }

.hero-tagline {
  font-size: clamp(36px, 7vw, 96px);
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: #fff;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
}
.hero-tagline .line { display: block; overflow: hidden; }
.hero-tagline .line span { display: inline-block; transform: translateY(120%); transition: transform 1.4s var(--ease-out-expo); }
.hero.loaded .hero-tagline .line span { transform: translateY(0); }

.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 17px);
  font-weight: 700;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 1s ease 0.7s;
  color: var(--gray);
  text-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
}
.hero.loaded .hero-sub { opacity: 1; }

.hero-scroll {
  position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 2;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 1s ease 1.2s forwards;
}
.hero-scroll span { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray); }
.scroll-line { width: 1px; height: 50px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.scroll-line::after { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -100%; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: var(--white); animation: scrollDown 2s ease infinite; }
@keyframes scrollDown { 0% { top: -100%; } 100% { top: 100%; } }
@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  canvas#fluid {
    transform: scaleX(-1) scaleY(-1);
  }
  .hero-logo-img { height: 100px; }
  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 8vw, 48px);
  }
}

/* ---- MISSION ---- */
.mission { padding: 0; position: relative; overflow: visible; }
.mission .section-title {
  font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 52px);
}
.mission .section-title .accent {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--magenta), var(--purple));
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
}

.mission .section-pad {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.mission .section-desc { text-align: left; }

/* ---- 産官学 DIAGRAM ---- */
.sangakukan-section {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 500px;
  margin-top: 60px;
  padding-bottom: 80px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(123,47,190,0.08) 0%, rgba(233,30,140,0.04) 30%, transparent 70%);
  border-radius: 24px;
  overflow: visible;
}

.sangakukan-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

/* Connecting lines */
.sangakukan-line {
  position: absolute;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--magenta), var(--blue));
  opacity: 0.3;
  transform-origin: left center;
}
.sangakukan-line.line-1 {
  width: 240px;
  top: 38%;
  left: calc(50% - 120px);
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--magenta), var(--blue));
  stroke-dasharray: 8 6;
}
.sangakukan-line.line-2 {
  width: 200px;
  top: 55%;
  left: calc(50% + 20px);
  transform: rotate(60deg);
  transform-origin: left center;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
}
.sangakukan-line.line-3 {
  width: 200px;
  top: 55%;
  right: calc(50% + 20px);
  transform: rotate(-60deg);
  transform-origin: right center;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--magenta));
}

/* Lines canvas */
.sangaku-lines-canvas {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

/* Circle nodes */
.sangakukan-node {
  position: absolute;
  width: 140px;
  height: 140px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  z-index: 2;
  cursor: default;
}
.sangakukan-node .node-kanji {
  font-size: 42px;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1;
}
.sangakukan-node .node-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  margin-top: 8px;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.5;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

/* Node positions — equilateral triangle: 産(top), 官(bottom-left), 学(bottom-right) */
.sangakukan-node.node-san {
  top: 8%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: rgba(233,30,140,0.12);
  box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(233,30,140,0.15), inset 0 0 30px rgba(233,30,140,0.05);
  animation: floatNode1 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.sangakukan-node.node-san .node-kanji { color: var(--magenta); }

.sangakukan-node.node-kan {
  bottom: 10%;
  left: calc(50% - 220px);
  background: rgba(48,79,254,0.12);
  box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(48,79,254,0.15), inset 0 0 30px rgba(48,79,254,0.05);
  animation: floatNode2 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.sangakukan-node.node-kan .node-kanji { color: var(--blue); }

.sangakukan-node.node-gaku {
  bottom: 10%;
  left: calc(50% + 80px);
  background: rgba(123,47,190,0.12);
  box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(123,47,190,0.15), inset 0 0 30px rgba(123,47,190,0.05);
  animation: floatNode3 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.sangakukan-node.node-gaku .node-kanji { color: var(--purple); }

/* Float animations */
@keyframes floatNode1 {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-12px); }
}
@keyframes floatNode2 {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
}
@keyframes floatNode3 {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-14px); }
}

/* Ripple effect */
.sangakukan-node::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: -20px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid currentColor;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: ripple 4.5s ease-out infinite;
}
.sangakukan-node.node-san::after { animation-delay: 0s; color: #E91E8C; }
.sangakukan-node.node-kan::after { animation-delay: 1.5s; color: #304FFE; }
.sangakukan-node.node-gaku::after { animation-delay: 3s; color: #7B2FBE; }

@keyframes ripple {
  0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
  100% { transform: scale(2.5); opacity: 0; }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .sangakukan-section { height: 420px; }
  .sangakukan-node { width: 110px; height: 110px; }
  .sangakukan-node .node-kanji { font-size: 32px; }
  .sangakukan-node .node-sub { font-size: 10px; }
  .sangakukan-node.node-san { top: 8%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .sangakukan-node.node-kan { left: calc(50% - 170px); }
  .sangakukan-node.node-gaku { left: calc(50% + 60px); }
}

/* ---- CONFERENCE ---- */
.conference-title-block { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 80px; }
.conference-main-title {
  font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 80px);
  font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.conference-main-title .gradient-text {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--magenta) 0%, var(--purple) 50%, var(--blue) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
}

.timeline { position: relative; padding: 0; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 700px; }

.timeline-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  position: relative;
}
.timeline-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.timeline-year {
  flex: 0 0 160px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  padding-right: 32px;
}

.timeline-year-number {
  font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 1;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  transition: color 0.6s var(--ease-out-expo);
}
.timeline-item.visible .timeline-year-number { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }

.timeline-content-link {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition: background 0.3s ease;
}
.timeline-content-link:hover {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.timeline-photo {
  width: 160px; height: 100px; flex-shrink: 0;
  object-fit: cover; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--dark-gray);
}
.timeline-text { flex: 1; text-align: left; }
.timeline-venue { font-size: clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 22px); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.timeline-detail { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.6; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .timeline-item { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  .timeline-year { flex: 0 0 auto; justify-content: flex-start; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .timeline-content-link { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  .timeline-photo { width: 120px; height: 75px; }
}

/* ---- BUSINESS AREAS ---- */
/* ---- BUSINESS — full-width image cards, stacked ---- */
.biz-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1px;
  margin-top: 60px;
}

.biz-card {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  min-height: 360px;
  background: var(--dark-gray);
  overflow: hidden;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: var(--white);
  transition: background 0.4s ease;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}
.biz-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.biz-card:hover { background: #1e1e1e; }
.biz-card:nth-child(even) { direction: rtl; }
.biz-card:nth-child(even) > * { direction: ltr; }

.biz-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.biz-img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s var(--ease-out-expo);
}
.biz-card:hover .biz-img {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}
/* Color overlay on image */
.biz-img-wrap::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  mix-blend-mode: soft-light;
}
.biz-card:hover .biz-img-wrap::after { opacity: 0.6; }
.biz-card[data-color="magenta"] .biz-img-wrap::after { background: var(--magenta); }
.biz-card[data-color="purple"] .biz-img-wrap::after { background: var(--purple); }
.biz-card[data-color="blue"] .biz-img-wrap::after { background: var(--blue); }
.biz-card[data-color="red"] .biz-img-wrap::after { background: var(--red); }
.biz-card[data-color="yellow"] .biz-img-wrap::after { background: var(--yellow); }

.biz-body {
  padding: 48px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: left;
}

.biz-name {
  font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 32px);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.biz-desc {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  line-height: 2;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.biz-arrow {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--magenta);
  opacity: 1;
  transform: none;
  transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-out-expo);
}
.biz-card:hover .biz-arrow {
  transform: translateX(4px);
}
.biz-arrow .external-icon {
  display: inline-block;
  vertical-align: -2px;
  margin-left: 2px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .biz-list { gap: 16px; }
  .biz-card,
  .biz-card:nth-child(even) {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    direction: ltr;
    min-height: 300px;
  }
  .biz-card { border-radius: 8px; border-bottom: none; }
  .biz-img-wrap { height: 200px; }
  .biz-body { padding: 32px 24px; }
}

/* ---- DIRECTORS ---- */
.directors-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 48px;
  margin-top: 48px;
  text-align: left;
}
.director-photo { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1/1; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; background: var(--dark-gray); }
.director-role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--magenta); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.director-name { font-size: clamp(20px, 2vw, 28px); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.director-bio { font-size: 13px; line-height: 2; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-weight: 300; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .directors-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; text-align: center; }
  .director-photo { width: 200px; margin: 0 auto 20px; }
  .director-role, .director-name { text-align: center; }
  .director-bio { text-align: left; }
}

/* ---- COMPANY INFO ---- */
.company-table {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 360px;
  margin: 48px auto 0;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  text-align: left;
}
.company-table th {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray);
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  padding: 18px 24px 18px 0;
  width: 120px;
  vertical-align: top;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.company-table td {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  padding: 18px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}
.company-table tr:last-child th,
.company-table tr:last-child td {
  border-bottom: none;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .company-table { max-width: 100%; }
  .company-table th { width: 80px; }
}

/* ---- FLUID SNAKE DIVIDER ---- */
.fluid-snake {
  width: 100%;
  height: 300px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: visible;
  z-index: 10;
  margin-top: -100px;
  margin-bottom: -100px;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.fluid-snake canvas {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  display: block;
}
.fluid-snake-fallback {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  position: relative;
  display: none;
}
.fluid-snake-fallback .snake-line {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: -100%;
  width: 200%;
  height: 4px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--magenta), var(--purple), var(--blue), var(--yellow), var(--red), var(--magenta));
  background-size: 50% 100%;
  animation: snakeMove 4s linear infinite;
  filter: blur(1px);
}
.fluid-snake-fallback .snake-line:nth-child(2) {
  top: calc(50% - 20px);
  height: 2px;
  opacity: 0.5;
  animation-delay: -1s;
  filter: blur(2px);
}
.fluid-snake-fallback .snake-line:nth-child(3) {
  top: calc(50% + 20px);
  height: 2px;
  opacity: 0.5;
  animation-delay: -2s;
  filter: blur(2px);
}
@keyframes snakeMove {
  0% { transform: translateX(0) translateY(0); }
  25% { transform: translateX(12.5%) translateY(-15px); }
  50% { transform: translateX(25%) translateY(0); }
  75% { transform: translateX(37.5%) translateY(15px); }
  100% { transform: translateX(50%) translateY(0); }
}

/* ---- CONTACT ---- */
.contact-section { text-align: center; position: relative; background: transparent; }
.contact-email {
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 26px); font-weight: 600;
  padding: 16px 48px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); border-radius: 60px;
  transition: all 0.4s var(--ease-out-expo);
  margin-top: 16px;
}
.contact-email:hover { background: var(--white); color: var(--black); border-color: var(--white); }

/* ---- GRADIENT LINE ---- */
.gradient-line {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 101;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--magenta), var(--purple), var(--blue), var(--yellow), var(--red));
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  animation: gradientShift 6s ease infinite;
}
@keyframes gradientShift { 0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; } 50% { background-position: 100% 50%; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="gradient-line"></div>

<!-- ===== HERO with WebGL Fluid Funnel ===== -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <canvas id="fluid"></canvas>

  <div class="hero-content">
    <img src="assets/images/logo-for-black-bg.png" alt="Designship" class="hero-logo-img">
    <h1 class="hero-tagline">
      <span class="line"><span>産業の未来を拓く</span></span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">一般社団法人デザインシップ</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll"><span>Scroll</span><div class="scroll-line"></div></div>
</section>

<!-- ===== MISSION ===== -->
<section class="mission" id="mission">
  <div class="section-pad">
    <p class="section-label reveal">ミッション</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal delay-1"><span class="accent">次世代の産業</span>に貢献する<br>デザイン人材の輩出。</h2>
    <p class="section-desc reveal delay-2">
      産業においてデザインの対象範囲や役割が拡張し、かつてないほどに重要視される世の流れに沿って、次世代におけるあるべきデザイン人材像を構想し、国民の創造性向上に寄与することを目的としています。2018年の設立以来、カンファレンス、教育、行政支援、企業研修、フリーランスコレクティブなど多角的な事業を展開しています。
    </p>

    <!-- 産官学連携 Diagram — Creative Glassmorphism -->
